  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Destroyers are the smallest military ship that are
  well-suited to offensive operations.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>They sometimes carry troops. They also usually include
  torpedo weapons for orbital bombardment.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Destroyers are well defended and well-armed. However th=
ey
  are not usually as fast or maneuverable as frigates</span>.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Destroyers are usually the largest military ship that y=
our
  empire can build at the start of a game. As your construction tech increa=
ses
  you will be able to build larger military ships like Cruisers and Capital
  Ships.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
